      <description>&lt;p&gt;In the &#xA;    &#xA;&#xA;&#xA;&#xA;&#xA;&#xA;&#xA;&#xA;&#xA;    &#xA;    &#xA;    &#xA;&#xA;&#xA;&#xA;    &#xA;        &lt;a href=&#34;http://localhost:1313/posts/thoughtsoninterviewing-1/&#34;&gt;first part&lt;/a&gt; of this series, I talked a little about how our industry interviews&#xA;currently and some of the issues I have with the current process. In this post, I want to talk a little more about what&#xA;we should be doing in interviews, and who we&amp;rsquo;re actually trying to hire.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
